<h2>Switches</h2>
<h3 class="subheader">See <a href="http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/components/switch.html">Foundation - Switches</a></h3>

<hr>

<h2>F-Switch</h2>
<p>For a single, toggleable switch, use \{{f-switch}} with a bound boolean value.</p>

<h3>Example</h3>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h4>Template</h4>
    <pre><code>\{{f-switch value=switchDemoValue}}</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h4>Rendered Component</h4>
    {{f-switch value=switchDemoValue}}
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<h3>F-Switch Properties</h3>

<dl>
  <dt>name <span class="label secondary">string</span></dt>
  <dd><code>name</code> attribute value for the switch.</dd>

  <dt>value <span class="label secondary">boolean</span></dt>
  <dd>Bound, toggleable value for the switch.</dd>
</dl>

<hr>

<h2>F-Switches</h2>
<p>For multiple exclusive options, and/or non-boolean value selections, use \{{f-switches}}.</p>

<h3>Example</h3>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h4>Template</h4>
    <pre><code>\{{f-switches
  name="switches-demo"
  options=switchesOptions
  value=switchDemoValue
}}</code></pre>

    <h4>Controller</h4>
    <pre><code>switchesOptions: [
  {
    id: 'a',
    label: 'Off',
    value: 'off'
  }, {
    id: 'a1',
    label: 'On',
    value: 'on'
  }
],

switchesValue: 'off'</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <h4>Rendered Component</h4>
    {{f-switches name="switches-demo" options=switchesOptions value=switchesValue}}
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<h3>F-Switches Properties</h3>

<dl>
  <dt>name <span class="label secondary">string</span></dt>
  <dd>Shared <code>name</code> attribute value for the switches.</dd>

  <dt>value <span class="label secondary">boolean</span></dt>
  <dd>Bound, shared, toggleable value for the switches.</dd>
</dl>
